    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps fitted with from one to four lenses to concentrate and intensify light, most commonly made of pewter or of tinned sheet iron with a separate glass font.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
